{"tid":157654,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友係閃電俠","createTime":"2017-03-15T16:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T09:28:52.000Z","uid":85944,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5774fb1d40aa13546b697acb794d1704eb731d1","tid":157654,"uid":85944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"第一次同男朋友搞野，估唔到佢咁快。<br />\n都唔知有無一分鐘，已經帶左套。<br />\n我無試過一分鐘可以過得咁快，我好想停留係呢一分鐘十分鐘。<br />\n咁我又覺得唔可以因爲以一次嘅經驗為準，就作判斷。<br />\n點知過左好多次都一樣。<br />\n我嚴重認為佢有早洩嘅問題，但係我又唔夠膽提出。<br />\n佢問我覺唔覺得佢快，我竟然答無，就咁我就講左人生第一次大話。<br />\n我心諗，會唔會試下用持久裝會好啲。<br />\n點知比我發現，佢一直買嘅已經係持久裝。<br />\n我又會諗，佢去買嘅時候會唔會有小小覺得柒？<br />\n我又會諗，究竟佢係咪一早已經識到自己嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n究竟我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6903472f123bcfa55946bedc1d8daf042186aaf","tid":157654,"uid":58820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"比我屌"},{"pid":"fb3261dfba2b1fe60ff11ebea0363835099ba1ad","tid":157654,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"你鬆唔鬆？<br />\n我around 30-40分鐘<br />\n可以教下你男朋友"},{"pid":"83023b0f7b24f580fe1f23a161e08b78093bd372","tid":157654,"uid":16111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"PM我幫下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 會買定特效持久裝"},{"pid":"8fb38356d633f022374d8285936252188a055f20","tid":157654,"uid":25250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你個菊花太緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fb74e780910ac5ffc7f0e3c6623226aca12e11","tid":157654,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"我就講左人生第一次大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3481f164111939436088c476262d0d486db27059","tid":157654,"uid":9489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep